OL,3,CCroydon named England's fly-tipping
OL,4,Chotspot with seven boroughs in top ten
OL,6,FSeven out of the ten worst areas for
OL,7,Ffly-tipping in the UK are in London,
OL,8,Fwith Croydon topping the table with
OL,9,Fover 53-thousand cases.
OL,11,FThe government figures relate to
OL,12,Frubbish illegally dumped on public
OL,13,Fland, with private landowners across
OL,14,Fthe country facing clear-up costs from
OL,15,Fthe scourge of having waste fly-tipped
OL,16,Fon their property.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
