OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772193824
OL,3,CCroydon named England's fly-tipping
OL,4,Chotspot with seven boroughs in top ten
OL,6,FLocal authorities in England recorded
OL,7,Fa 9% rise in fly-tipping incidents in
OL,8,F2024/2025 from the 1.15 million they
OL,9,Fhad to deal with in 2023/2024, and the
OL,10,Fhighest figures since new methods for
OL,11,Frecording cases were introduced in
OL,12,F2018/2019.
OL,14,FThe top ten worst areas are:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
