PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772193824
OL,3,CCroydon named England's fly-tipping
OL,4,Chotspot with seven boroughs in top ten
OL,6,FFly-tipping most commonly occurs on
OL,7,Fpavements and roads, accounting for
OL,8,Fmore than a third of cases (37%),
OL,9,Faccording to the figures, and almost a
OL,10,Fthird of incidents (31%) were the size
OL,11,Fof a small van load, while 27% were
OL,12,Fthe equivalent to a car boot or less.
OL,14,FDepartment for Environment, Food and
OL,15,FRural Affairs Minister Mary Creagh
OL,16,Fsaid: "We are empowering local
OL,17,Fauthorities to clamp down on waste
OL,18,Fcowboys and restore pride in our local
OL,19,Fareas.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772193824
OL,3,CCroydon named England's fly-tipping
OL,4,Chotspot with seven boroughs in top ten
OL,6,F"I share the public's fury at seeing
OL,7,Four streets, parks and fields used as
OL,8,Fdumping grounds.
OL,10,F"Fly-tippers should know ` if you use
OL,11,Fyour van to trash our countryside,
OL,12,Fdon't be surprised when it ends up on
OL,13,Fthe scrapheap.
OL,15,FShe added: "This Government is
OL,16,Finvesting in cutting-edge technology
OL,17,Fand boosting Environment Agency
OL,18,Ffunding to put more waste crime
OL,19,Fofficers on the ground, while
OL,20,Fintroducing tougher checks and
OL,21,Fpenalties for those who break the law."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@LOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
