PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772193824
OL,3,CCroydon named England's fly-tipping
OL,4,Chotspot with seven boroughs in top ten
OL,6,FAs the figures were announced, Defra
OL,7,Fpublished new guidance to help
OL,8,Fcouncils seize and crush more vehicles
OL,9,Fused for fly-tipping, or repurpose
OL,10,Fthem for clean-up operations, along
OL,11,Fwith advice on how to take cases to
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,FCouncils are also being urged to name
OL,15,Fand shame fly-tippers on social media.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/5
